OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloud and rain slowly clear the
OL,6,Fsoutheast through the morning,
OL,7,Fbrightening from the west with some
OL,8,Fsunny spells. Western areas stay
OL,9,Fmostly bright, though sharp showers
OL,10,Facross northern areas this afternoon.
OL,11,FFeeling a little cooler than of late.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FSome dry, clear spells for
OL,14,Fmany at first. Then a band of locally
OL,15,Fheavy rain moves into western areas
OL,16,Fthrough the early hours. Turning
OL,17,Fbreezier too. Remaining mainly frost
OL,18,Ffree.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
