OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FLocally heavy rain and brisk
OL,6,Fwinds moving east through the morning.
OL,7,FTurning drier but remaining rather
OL,8,Fcloudy through the afternoon before
OL,9,Ffurther rain arrives in the northwest
OL,10,Flater. Feeling milder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
